description: Laravel + Inertia + React stack and boundaries for this repo
alwaysApply: true
---

# Stack

- Backend: Laravel 9, PHP 8.0+
- Frontend: React 17, Inertia.js (@inertiajs/inertia-react), Vite (laravel-vite-plugin)
- UI: Ant Design (antd), Tailwind available; follow existing pages first
- Routes in JS: prefer Ziggy (`route()`) where the project already uses it

# Structure

- Inertia pages: `resources/js/Pages/`
- Shared components: `resources/js/Components/`, `resources/js/Shared/`
- Path alias: `@/` maps to `resources/js/` (match existing imports)

# Conventions

- Match existing file style (this repo uses `.js`/`.jsx`, not TypeScript unless a file already is).
- Reuse existing helpers (e.g. under `resources/js/Helpers/`) instead of new utilities when possible.
- Do not upgrade major versions (Laravel, Inertia, React, antd) in a normal task unless explicitly requested.

# New dependencies

- Do not add npm or Composer packages without explicit user approval; prefer built-in Laravel / existing packages.
